---
title: Bacon and Cheese-Stuffed Turkey with Potato Wedges and Salad
description: At HelloFresh, we love stuffed turkey! In this variation, cheese and bacon-stuffed turkey breasts get an upgrade with a crispy coating that combines two types of breadcrumbs for added texture. Classic roasted potatoes are served alongside to round out the meal.
